Query and scrape the NYC Water Payment history website.

author :  Luigi Patruno
date : Nov 21-22, 2015

3rd party packages used:
	mechanize - to submit HTML forms
	BeautifulSoup - to parse HTML response
	pandas - organize payment data

Text file:
    - account_numbers.txt: contains block, lot, name, address and account number (ALL PUBLIC DATA)
    - payments.txt : contains all info in account_numbers.txt and a payment history (ALL PUBLIC DATA)

These data are available at:
http://nycserv.nyc.gov/NYCServWeb/WaterChargeHistorySearch.jsp
